content.rendered:
Directed by Manjari Makijany

Written by Manjari Makijany. Vinati Makijany. Michael Pellico

Cast Waheeda Rehman(Maharani). Amy Maghera(Jessica). Anurag Arora(Mahesh). Jonathan Readwin(Erick). Rachel Saanchita Gupta(Prerna). Sahidur Rahaman(Police officer). Kamlesh Gill(Dadi). Shafin Patel(Ankush). Emmanuel Pappas(Skater Judge #2). Swati Das(Shanti). Vinayak Gupta(Subodh). Ambrish Saxena(Ramkesh). Janthavy Norton(Self – skater). Ankit Yadav(Vikram (as Ankit Rao)). Shraddha Gaikwad(Gunjan). Anish Christopher Kevin(Self – skater). Abhi Shek(Self – skater). Sohan Suhalka(Vishwanath). Darius Bharucha(Self – skater). Atita Verghese(Self – skater). Jacob Wiese(Self – skater). Vivek Yadav(Tipu)

Languages English. Hindi

Producers David U. Lee. Manjari Makijany. Vinati Makijany. Emmanuel Pappas. Michael Pellico.

Production Leeding Media. Mac Productions. Skatepark Films
